formatted_address: 1220 ECP, #01-23 East Coast Lagoon Food Village, Singapore 468960
name: Tong Shui Local Delights

reviews.text:
Ordered hokkien mee and char kway teow.
Both are tasteless, will be my last time eating from the stall. Dont understand y the q is long. I joined the q cos i tot was nice, total regret.

Food was not bad but owner attitude is horrible. Rude and stingy. Ordered 2 largest plate of food and was only given 2 small paper plates to share among the group. When asked for 2 more paper plates, owner replied “You only buy 2 plates, you want so many small plates for what”.

vicinity: 1220 East Coast Parkway, #01-23 East Coast Lagoon Food Village
